# ADR-006: Automated Testing Strategy

## Status

Accepted

## Context

VS Code extensions depend on APIs unavailable outside the editor runtime.

The project requires automated validation.

## Decision

Jest will be used for unit testing.

VS Code APIs will be mocked.

The test strategy covers:

- Commands
- Services
- Database connectors
- AI integrations

## Consequences

Positive:

- Faster development feedback
- Safer refactoring
- Better code quality

Negative:

- Mock maintenance required
